# {{lb|en|uncountable|British|NZ|accounting}} The function of compiling and providing financial information primarily by reports referred to as financial statements. Accounting includes bookkeeping, systems design, analysis and interpretation of accounting information.
# {{lb|en|countable|accounting}} A company or organisation that performs such a function.

